snippet.title: Nascar Racing 4 - Crashes from the past
snippet.description: Felt like doing something from an older game and Nascar Racing 4 met that requirement, lol. Had to work with what I had since CCM doesn't work for N4. Btw the cars are from the old web site, High-Compression.com
